**LIX Calculator:** https://www.skrivguiden.se/verktyg/lix

**Input:**

* Number of letters in the text: 353
* Number of words in the text: 74
* Number of sentences in the text: 14

**Formula:**

```
LIX = (Number of letters / Number of words) + (Number of sentences / Number of words) * 100
```

**Calculation:**

```
LIX = (353 / 74) + (14 / 74) * 100
```

```
LIX = 4.77 + 18.92
```

```
LIX = 23.69
```

**Result:**

LIX = 23.69